longBusinessSummary: BioPower Operations Corporation, through its subsidiaries, focuses on operating HyFi Platform in the United States. The HyFi Platform offers HyFi Decentralized Finance (DeFi) exchange marketplace using blockchain platform technology. Its DeFi priciples offers financial services utilizing tokenization and non-fungible tokens. BioPower Operations Corporation was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Aventura, Florida.
